标题: 急急急！这个是怎么回事啊！只有这点钱了！开了服务器就出现一段话*** 启动服务端中 ***
[14:41:06] [Server thread/INFO]: Starting minecraft server version 1.7.10
[14:41:06] [Server thread/INFO]: Loading properties
[14:41:06] [Server thread/INFO]: Default game type: SURVIVAL
[14:41:06] [Server thread/INFO]: Generating keypair
[14:41:07] [Server thread/INFO]: Starting Minecraft server on 219.134.24.20:63921
[14:41:08] [Server thread/WARN]: **** FAILED TO BIND TO PORT!
[14:41:08] [Server thread/WARN]: The exception was: java.net.BindException: Cannot assign requested address: bind
[14:41:08] [Server thread/WARN]: Perhaps a server is already running on that port?
[14:41:08] [Server thread/INFO]: Stopping server
*** 服务端已停止 ***

翻译以后是这样的
* * *启动服务端中* * *
　　[14:41:06][服务器线程/信息):开始minecraft卖出1.7.10服务器版本
　　[14:41:06][服务器线程/信息]:加载属性
　　[14:41:06][服务器线程/信息]:默认游戏类型:生存
　　[14:41:06][服务器线程/信息):生成密钥对
　　[14:41:07][服务器线程/信息):开始Minecraft卖出219.134.24.20:63921服务器
　　[14:41:08][服务器线程/警告):* * * *没有绑定到端口!
　　[14:41:08][服务器线程/警告]:例外是:java.net.BindException:不能分配请求的地址

求大神教啊
